# packages/* conventions

## Allowed dependencies

- `runtime-oss` → `@claw-dashboard/runtime-contracts` only
- `database` → Prisma client only
- `workspace-sync` → Node fs/path; **no** `@nestjs/*`

## Forbidden in packages/*

- `@nestjs/common`, `@nestjs/core`, Fastify, Express adapters
- Import from `apps/api` or `apps/web`

## Nest exceptions stay in apps/api

- `BadRequestException`, guards, cookies → map errors at app boundary
